FirstRand Still Looking to Purchase Nigerian Bank, Business Day Says

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-06-07T05:26:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/firstrand-still-looking-to-purchase-nigerian-bank-business-day-says.html
FirstRand Ltd. (FSR)  is looking into other
opportunities to buy a bank in  Nigeria  after talks about
acquiring a majority stake in the country’s Sterling Bank Plc
ended unsuccessfully, Business Day reported, citing Sam Moss,
FirstRand’s head of investor relations.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
